    • Constructor Detail

      • Plane

        public Plane(int aTime,
             char landingOrTakeOff)
        Initialize a Plane with a specified initial time and status character.
        Parameters:
        aTime - the integer value of time (ex, minute) that the plane arrived
        landingOrTakeOff - a character value representing the type of operation the plane is doing If landingOrTakeOff is 'L' it means the plane is landing If landingOrTakeOff is 'T' it means Taking off.
